Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:45.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#19 羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這粒子束是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 捕捉目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將三架Gundam Throne判定為助長紛爭的對象 開始武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些人 這些機體 能算得上是… Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.87,0:00:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 約翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽見嗎 Exia的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何妨礙我們的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了根除戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神錯亂了嗎 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米迦勒 應戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞·艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue 破壞目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia在和Throne作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才 Virtue似乎也已參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連提耶利亞都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam居然自相殘殺 搞不好可能兩敗俱傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不可 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trinity的做法太氣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜一個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們的行動也可能是計劃中的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的行動或許也在計劃之內
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·史特拉特斯發來緊急密信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知他盡可能阻止戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 視現場情況 尊重他本人的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實質上不就是隨他便的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可有損戰術預報員的大名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亞呢 出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下保護普特萊瑪奧斯 事到如今 這裏也不安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然心裏癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小屁孩真會惹麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 沒阻止 沒阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過托他的福 Miss.皇也下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 剎那的心情也不難理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想成為Gundam本身 成為肩負根除紛爭大任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我正躍躍欲試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  洛克昂·史特拉特斯 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 Exia攻擊新型Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可難說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅龍 我呢 只要這個世界有所改變就無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論用什麼手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比預想的要快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三階段的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已無路可退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣型S32
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 沒想到會有和你配合陣型的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia Virtue 持續和Throne交戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎使用了戰術陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S32 D07 還有F52
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞和剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 合體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真以為別人只會傻看著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你這機動性可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 機體控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統失靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受 好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有鏈接到Veda的機體都在其控制之下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam Nadleeh真正的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞·艾迪被特別授予的 對Gundam Meister的審判系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:09.97,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trial System
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不配做Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判定 罪該萬死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審判系統居然被強制解除了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7 領域中有部分數據被篡改了 這個數據區域到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連我都無法訪問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就是三對三了 要有公平競爭的精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰怕誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米迦勒 妮娜 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam自相殘殺 會影響計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們相比 你應該有更重要的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 尼爾·狄蘭提
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾…狄蘭提？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我的數據…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過Veda閱覽過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7 的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 你在成為Gundam Meister之前 想要復仇的對象一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:08:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯共和國的反政府游擊組織—KPSA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個組織的成員中 有一個名叫索蘭·易卜拉欣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？這人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭·易卜拉欣 代號 剎那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是剎那？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他就是殺死你雙親和妹妹的那個組織成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的仇敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七架Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經束手無策了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續作戰讓軍隊疲乏的話 我們陣營的經濟將會崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 不如接受他們的要求解除武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做的話 各國的統一性會瓦解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天人」的相關人士通過網絡謀求與我們聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還附帶了組織內部的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 內部分裂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝似乎還未拋棄我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭到攻擊的IRIS公司的工場廢墟處 聚集了眾多遇害者家屬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一片凝重的氣氛包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據稱發動攻擊的三架MS 是新型Gundam 對於其過激行為…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲 鮮花 我就放在這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 回日本去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翹課可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你來照顧 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也不能一直這樣下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把路易絲一個人丟下回去什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈的夢想不是在宇宙裏工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因為我而讓沙慈放棄夢想啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在待在一起 過後只會更傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直感覺愧疚的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓沙慈後悔終身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 把我的夢想托付給沙慈好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 請實現我的夢想吧 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:46.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}さよなら　言葉じゃ繋げやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:54.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}僕らのミライが　離ればなれに歩き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:12:02.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}君という　光が映し出した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:10.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}ココロの片隅　行き場を探すユメ達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}Love for a day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.59,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}華やぐ日も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:25.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}静かに痛む夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:33.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}隠せない胸の奥の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:43.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}傷痕を解き放て
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}Love Today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.59,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}コタエはずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:57.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}見慣れた景色の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:08.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}Love Today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:21.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}Learn to love today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:30.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\an8}Learn to love today
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:46.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N再見僅憑言語並無法緊密相連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:54.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N我們的未來將漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:12:02.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N你的光芒映照著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:10.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N心中的角落  尋求歸宿的諸多夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.59,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N喧囂的時日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:25.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N寂靜痛楚的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:33.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N將心中無法隱藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:43.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N傷痕  釋放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:49.59,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N答案總會在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:57.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}\N這習以為常的景色中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏睡著可是會著涼的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？你…你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該男孩子先自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那個… 我是沙慈·庫斯洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲·阿勒威 請多指教哦 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上來就直呼姓名？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 也不是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 勞煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是拉格納·哈維啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁懸浮列車事業的總裁 國際經濟團體的頭頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既有建造MS的財力 也可以自由使用軌道升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 採訪還是見好就收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢 對方可是我們的大股東啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太歲頭上動土是沒啥好結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才暗地調查啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會放棄的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得找到了線索
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是KPSA所屬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫爾吉斯出身？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游擊隊的少年士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 Trinity說的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母和妹妹死於KPSA的自殺性恐怖炸彈襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都起因於太陽能發電計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界規模的石油出口管制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是讓我們放棄依賴化石燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但受影響最大的是中東各國
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為出口管制導致國家經濟崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國民貧困不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飢不擇食的人將精神寄托於真主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽從真主代言人的言論
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是些追求財富地位的膚淺之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是導致了那場長達20餘年的太陽能發電紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真主土地上居民們的聖戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 單方面決定採取出口管制的國聯也非善類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 並非真主或者宗教的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽能發電系統也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 世界肯定會在其中扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括你是被KPSA利用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持續進行著違心的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是由於受到這扭曲世界的波及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了家人 完完全全的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 接受成為Meister的現實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道這是矛盾的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的所作所為與恐怖活動無異
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去斬斷引發暴力的鎖鏈 而是選擇了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是為了阻止那樣的悲劇重演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要從根本上徹底改變這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有壓倒性的力量 就能在世界上形成抑制力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界後甘願接受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在此之前我還有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 我現在幾乎克制不住想射殺你的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我為家人報仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我釋怨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾相信真主 被迫相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是你的錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上沒有真主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界上沒有真主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算不上回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信真主 然後得知沒有真主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KPSA的領導者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿爾·薩謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿利·阿爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薩謝斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在莫拉尼亞所屬PMC
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民間軍事企業？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹完游擊隊然後去當傭兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是單純的戰爭中毒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.92,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在莫拉尼亞的戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來當時走出駕駛艙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是希望確認他的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道他的真主在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他心中沒有真主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我…至今為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算用Exia做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我射殺的話你就無法如願了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能代替我實現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我改變這個扭曲的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我還活著 我會繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非作為索蘭·易卜拉欣 而是作為天人的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太一本正經 讓人開槍都沒心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是個了不起的Gundam傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最高級別的讚譽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:07.20,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}非洲大陸 西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到啊 竟會受到Gundam的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還親了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求Ragna下達指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視情況 可能會再次與Gundam交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:31.94,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}南極大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ笑顔してた　そんな僕らも　幾年も重ね過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う景色を　受け入れられずに　もがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れちゃいけないから Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:22:00.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この広い大地と仲間達のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經久不變的笑顏　是這樣的我們　在年輪中週而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦身而過的風景　卻無法剪下收藏　唯心房中絲縷焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將無謂的自尊遠遠拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用溫柔將這個世界抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告訴我你的勇氣　即使逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一個人便無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那一日的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於我心深處　只步未移
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因為不能忘記 Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:22:00.93,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這片無垠大地和同伴們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大幅度計劃變更造成世界平衡的劇變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其中 有人流淚 有人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至生命的最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.84,0:22:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 變革之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此份苦惱 誰人能知

